The paper deals with the application of deep transfer learning methods for the classification of colon cancer in confocal laser microscopy images. This involves the use of computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer science (cs.CV). The use of deep learning methods for classification also suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). Additionally, the paper involves the use of information retrieval techniques for feature extraction, which could place it under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
